# db_url:A connection string (DSN) used by SQLAlchemy to connect to your database.

# jwt_secret:Secret key used to sign JWT tokens,
#When user logs in → token is created using this secret
#When user sends request → token is verified using same secret
#If this leaks → anyone can generate valid tokens → your auth is dead.

#jwt_algo:Algorithm used to sign JWT
#Symmetric → same secret used for sign + verify
#Common, fast, but depends entirely on secret safety